node.text: Yesterday I lost my Aunt Pat (actually my great aunt, the last of her generation). She was one of my favorite people, always ready with a joke, a song, a jig & a hug. Here she is singing to the love of her life, my Uncle Bill, shortly before we lost him 2 yrs ago. Love you, Pat.❤️

node.text: So many people are asking how they can see #TheSuicideSquad early. Well, you’re invited to #YouDontKnowSquad, an exclusive screening of #TheSuicideSquad, followed by an NSFW Q&A with me and the cast! Reserve your seats while supplies last: link in bio! #DontGetTooAttached

node.text: Me & #Blackguard #PeteDavidson on the Belle Reve Prison set of #TheSuicideSquad. I love this guy & felt a great affinity with him from the 1st time we talked. He’s a remarkable talent who is fantastic in the movie, despite his werewolf phobia.

node.text: On most movies makeup artists are constantly dabbing the sweat off actors. On #TheSuicideSquad, has a gritty, grounded look, and which takes place in the hot jungle climate of Corto Maltese, we had to constantly keep the actors sweated up and dirty. Here’s @johncena getting his pits dampened by a pro.
